OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fantidepressants help       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fchronic pain               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People with chronic pain are being     
OL,6, given antidepressants with very little 
OL,7, scientific proof the medication helps, 
OL,8, a major review has found.              
OL,10,FIn studies, with nearly 30,000         
OL,11,Fpatients, there was "moderate" evidence
OL,12,Ffor only one drug, duloxetine, and just
OL,13,Ffor short-term pain relief.            
OL,15,FAnd there was a "shocking" lack of     
OL,16,Flong-term data, even though the pills  
OL,17,Fare usually prescribed for many months.
OL,19,FBut patients are advised to stay on    
OL,20,Fmedication if it works for them.       
